  • Constructor Details

    • Student_Research

      public Student_Research(String firstName, String lastName, long id)
      Parameterized Constructor of Student_Research class

      This constructor is used to represent and initialize the student research object.

      Precondition - The value of first name and last name must be a string and the value of id must be a valid long value.
      Postcondition - A student research object is created with the variables set to their parameter values, and enrollment type set to 'R'.
      Parameters:
      firstName - The first name of student research object.
      lastName - The last name of student research object.
      id - The identifier value of student research object.
